CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 27, 1957, pg. 3 reads: " 'Cool, Man, Cool!' - And you can't tell Fred Gearman, Randolph Davis, Roscoe Woods, William Gray and Alonzo Davis Jr. that they aren't just that with their "cool Ivy look", as they wind their way to Sunday school, on Bennett St., Easter Sunday morning. Their dress is typical of that worn by "their set" in the holiday parade of fashions."
TitMainTitle: Fred Gearman, Randolph Davis, Roscoe Woods, William Gray ,and Alonzo Davis Jr., walking down Bennett Street on Easter Sunday
